_sText:
This map has a pool, armory, greenhouse, cafeteria/kitchen, solitary, bar, pool, medic, race track, gun toss, and soccer. There are secret guns and teleports scattered around it. 

Lots of thanks to Tophattwaffle for his realworldtextures pack. His gamebanana page:http://gamebanana.com/members/144386
I also used Dasmatze's road textures:http://gamebanana.com/hl2/textures/897
